===Proper noun===
'''Abe'''

# Short form of the male [[given name]] ''[[Abraham]]''.

[[Category:Names]]
[[Category:English proper nouns]]


Short form of the male given name Abraham. A debate comando supremo, Abe so cool that he is almost Korean. He had been wandering the village of Glenview, Illinois, wallowing in his status of defector of the H-F team when he was picked up by GBS. South took him in reluctantly, only after witnessing his RiMal abilities. More intimidating than Max Voldman and more powerful than the Beast, Abe truly is a fearsome debate. He is known to be able to take on 8000 chinese Winstons at once and not break a sweat. Undoubtedly, Abe is more fearsome than Chuck Norris, for his roundhouse kick stands no chance to the power of Abe's silver-tongued spreading abilities. Abe, however, does not like cheese. At all.